For Windows : 
1. Download C# extensions. Then download and Install Dotnet. If you see VS Code giving you popup to install dotnet open it and install dotnet
2. Then in the folder run : "dotnet new console" then run : "dotnet restore"
3. Open automatically created Program.cs file and paste this code : 

using System;
namespace abc{
class Program
{
	public static void Main(string[] args)
	{
		Console.WriteLine("Hellaao");
	}
}

}

then run "dotnet build" and then "dotnet run" to execute the program
